WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.080 --> 00:00:03.260
Even in the afternoon, it keeps raining in Japan

00:00:03.880 --> 00:00:04.800
'Hello~'

00:00:05.340 --> 00:00:09.460
HyunJin is filming diligently despite the rain!

00:00:10.240 --> 00:00:11.200
'Do you like rain?'

00:00:11.700 --> 00:00:12.680
'Nope!'

00:00:14.220 --> 00:00:16.780
'I like watching the rain in my home but don’t like to go out when it’s raining'

00:00:16.780 --> 00:00:19.420
'My hair becomes frizzy when it rains…'

00:00:19.420 --> 00:00:20.500
'Like a female ghost!'

00:00:20.500 --> 00:00:21.540
(She's acting like a ghost)

